{"tid":1999832,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國媒體報道白宮正在制定向中國索賠方案","createTime":"2020-05-03T12:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T03:15:52.000Z","uid":141151,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5d183c5150b48ca9155f7996201c91edc9d018b6","tid":1999832,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:19:47.000Z","msg":"美國媒體報道白宮正在制定向中國索賠方案<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200502-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B4%A2%E8%B3%A0%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20200502-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25AE%25AE%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjghjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=54ff9f1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200502-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B4%A2%E8%B3%A0%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普政府高級官員透露，由於中國政府隱瞞新冠病毒爆發的真相，導致病毒在美國蔓延造成嚴重人命死亡和經濟損失，目前白宮正在制訂懲罰北京的方案，包括向中國提出經濟索賠。 <br />\n<br />\n據《華盛頓郵報》、CNN等美國媒體報道，政府多部門從4月30日開始舉行會議，制定對中國的懲罰方案，情報部門也參與了這一工作。方案包括取消中國所持有的美國國債、制定新的美中貿易政策等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報道說，總統特朗普近日對中國憤怒不已，批評中國隱瞞疫情給美國和世界造成災難。特朗普在白宮疫情簡報會上表示，美國將會向中國索取數以千億美元計的賠償，並說他正在考慮其他懲罰中國的措施。特朗普和助理私下已討論過取消中國的主權豁免，以便讓美國政府和疫情受害人可以起訴中國索賠。官員也討論了取消對中國所持部分美國國債的償付，但白宮官員表示這些初步想法變成正式工作還沒開始。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n在4月30日會議召開前，特朗普4月29日接受媒體採訪，被問到他是否正考慮使用關稅甚至勾銷中國所持美債時，特朗普沒有具體說明，只說&ldquo;我可以做很多事情，我們正在調查發生了甚麼。&rdquo;白宮高級顧問庫什納當天亮相福克斯（Fox）電視&ldquo;福克斯和朋友&rdquo;節目，強調特朗普&ldquo;他要求我們認真調查來龍去脈，病毒如何傳到美國，並保證他將採取任何必要的措施向造成問題的人追責。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"2e168a1c8de8f11e023fc4abba1e8eaded239759","tid":1999832,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"帳單一定流流長，幾世支共子女還唔完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdcb2ee92ede8fe69d0b5d9eaad5b019204da2e","tid":1999832,"uid":110456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDsJEn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDsJEn5.jpg&h=e4843430&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUAWeWs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUAWeWs.jpg&h=7d60efe6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VGSmq28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGSmq28.jpg&h=d548bef9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/im9Dtgu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fim9Dtgu.jpg&h=f2eb4e12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NBEHauR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNBEHauR.jpg&h=5514176c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CNVCJPR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNVCJPR.jpg&h=5f28594f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y9yMB9S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy9yMB9S.png&h=8bbdadb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"387ad343096b7b712773301fb0ba167faad97eeb","tid":1999832,"uid":356542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d183c5150b48ca9155f7996201c91edc9d018b6","tid":1999832,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:19:47.000Z","msg":"美國媒體報道白宮正在制定向中國索賠方案<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200502-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%B6%E5%AE%9