）電視&ldquo;福克斯和朋友&rdquo;節目，強調特朗普&ldquo;他要求我們認真調查來龍去脈，病毒如何傳到美國，並保證他將採取任何必要的措施向造成問題的人追責。&rdquo;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:45:18.000Z","msg":"美國死多啲人就可以索賠多啲<br />\n咁其實佢唔洗點做咩防疫 <br />\n等啲老弱嘅人死多啲 慳醫藥費之餘<br />\n又好啲問中國攞錢<br />\n一舉兩得<br />\ntrump真係做得幾醒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:48:56.000Z","msg":"到時歐英可以群體免疫，冇疫苗都唔驚，反面香港就繼續半封港，唔知封到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:02:02.000Z","msg":"咁幾好呀 群體免疫即係唔會有病啦<br />\n咁香港咪唔洗封關囉"},{"pid":"0192aed85da5eb98c221b392358c1ee8127a280c","tid":1999832,"uid":265485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02f788636d350a8ed0f7a4912f8790cba9d857e6","tid":1999832,"uid":356542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"149af6faf6ef2655ee8708edf4e8971156953ad4","tid":1999832,"uid":265485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"387ad343096b7b712773301fb0ba167faad97eeb","tid":1999832,"uid":356542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T12:45:18.000Z","msg":"美國死多啲人就可以索賠多啲<br />\n咁其實佢唔洗點做咩防疫 <br />\n等啲老弱嘅人死多啲 慳醫藥費之餘<br />\n又好啲問中國攞錢<br />\n一舉兩得<br />\ntrump真係做得幾醒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:48:56.000Z","msg":"到時歐英可以群體免疫，冇疫苗都唔驚，反面香港就繼續半封港，唔知封到幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:02:02.000Z","msg":"咁幾好呀 群體免疫即係唔會有病啦<br />\n咁香港咪唔洗封關囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:03:31.000Z","msg":"人地歐美就係，亞洲繼續爆，慢性經濟衰退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f026cd8ada2b8f065c21ee76b326baf05bf6dcbb","tid":1999832,"uid":356542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"149af6faf6ef2655ee8708edf4e8971156953ad4","tid":1999832,"uid":265485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"387ad343096b7b712773301fb0ba167faad97eeb","tid":1999832,"uid":356542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0